2007-05-29  Vitaly Alexeev <tishka92@yahoo.com>

	fixed bug #1727294 
	* gameswf/gameswf_environment.*: parse_path() is static now,
	it's useful outside of class too
	* gameswf/gameswf_character.*: added find_target()
	* gameswf/gameswf_sprite.cpp: removed set_text_value from set_member(),
	first: reduces performance, second: VAR from text field is a link to 
	variable in sprite_instance therefore we need to get it value in advance() time
	* gameswf/gameswf_text.*: if VAR is set then 
	- set_text_value() assigns text value to new text & call VAR->set_member()
	- get_text_value() gets text value from VAR->get_member()
	if VAR is changed outside of text_field then text_field gets new text value in
	advance()

2007-05-29  Vitaly Alexeev <tishka92@yahoo.com>

	* base/tu_config.h,
	* gameswf/gameswf.h,
	* gameswf/gameswf_font.*,
