	* gameswf/gameswf_sprite.cpp,
	* gameswf/gameswf_text.cpp,
	* gameswf/gameswf_freetype.*,
	* gameswf/win32/VC7/gameswf.vcproj: 
	the support of dynamic(not embedded) fonts is added (not completed yet).
	It is based on freetype library
	
