	* gameswf/gameswf_sprite.*: added goto_frame(const as_value& target_frame)
	
2007-05-24  Vitaly Alexeev <tishka92@yahoo.com>

	* gameswf/gameswf_as_sprite.cpp: applied the patch from Francois Guibert,
	fixed gotoAndPlay & gotoAndStop bug, Flash tries to convert STRING to NUMBER,
	if the conversion is OK then Flash uses this NUMBER as target_frame,
	else uses STRING as label of target_frame

