	* gameswf/gameswf_dlist.*: added remove_display_object(character* ch) that is used 
	to unload movie
	* gameswf/gameswf_environment.* rewritten load_file().
	During loadMovie(".jpg", ...), loadMovie(".3ds", ...) & unloadMovie() new empty 
	sprite_instance	is't created and target is used as new sprite_instance. 
	* gameswf/gameswf_impl.*: added MetaData tag reader

